quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  11,110,"Mazima twawa Musa ekitabo ne kyawukanwamu, singa si kigambo ekyava ewa Mukama omulabiriziwo ekyakulembera, eggoye lyandisaliddwawo (nebazikirira) era mazima bo bali mu kubuusabuusa era nga batankana (ku nsonga ya Kur’ani)"
  11,111,"Na mazima ddala bonna Mukama omulabiriziwo agenda kubasasula emirimu gya bwe mu bujjuvu, mazima yye amanyidde ddala bye bakola"
  11,112,"Kale beera mwesimbu nga bwolagiddwa, n'abo abeenenyezza naawe era temubeera ba kiwagi, anti mazima ye (Katonda) bye mukola abiraba"
  11,113,"Era temuggweranga ku abo abeeyisa obubi, omuliro negubakwata ate nga ojjeeko Katonda temulinaayo bayambi balala, era temugenda kutaasibwa"
  11,114,Era yimirizaawo e sswala ku nsalosalo ebbiri ez'emisana (ku makya n'akawungezi) n'ekiseera ekisooka ku kiro mazima ebirungi bijjawo ebibi. Okwo nno kubuulirira eri abo abajjukira
  11,115,"Era gumiikiriza, bulijjo Katonda tayinza butasasula mpeera ya bakozi ba bulungi"
  11,116,"Singa waaliyo mu mirembe egyabakulembera abantu abalina kye baasigazaawo (mu ddiini) nga bagaana obwonoonefu mu nsi, (tebaaliyo) okugyako batono nnyo mu abo be twawonya mu bo. Wabula bo abeeyisa obubi ne batwalibwa ebirungi bye baaweebwa mu nsi nebaba aboonoonyi"
  11,117,Mukama omulabiriziwo tabangako wa kuzikiriza ebitundu mu bulyazaamaanyi nga ate abantu baabyo bakozi ba bulungi
  11,118,"Singa Mukama omulabiriziwo yayagala, abantu bonna yandibafudde ekibiina kimu, naye tebagenda kuva ku kwawukana"
  11,119,"Okugyako oyo Mukama omulabiriziwo gwaba asaasidde. N'olwekyo kyeyava abatonda, era kyakakata ekigambo kya Mukama omulabiriziwo nti ngenda kujjuza omuliro Jahannama nga nzija mu majinni n'abantu okutwalira awamu"
  11,120,"Era tukutegeeza buli kimu ekikwata ku babaka, ekyo kyetunyweza nakyo omutima gwo, era mu kino ojjiddwa amazima n'okubuulirira, era nga kya kujjukiza eri abakkiriza"
  11,121,Era gamba abo abakkiriza nti mukolere ku nkola ya mmwe naffe katukole
  11,122,Era mulindirire naffe tulindiridde
  11,123,"Kandi kuri Allah ni iby'ibintu bitagaragara by'ijuru n'isi kandi kuri we azasubizwa icyo kibazo, byose, bityo rero musenge kandi umwishingikirize. Kandi Umwami wawe ntabwo azi ibyo ukora"